event: WelCome Party of Govt Muncipal Graduate College(GMGC) Faisalabad
detail: At Govt Muncipal Graduate College Faisalabad, we believe in beginning your academic journey with a bang! Our annual Welcome Party is more than just an event; it's a celebration of new beginnings, fresh friendships, and the start of your incredible college life.
